trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class encapsulates the transport security settings for queued transports.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
The existing instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class, to be used in initializing the new instance.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class, using an existing instance.
<paramref name="other" /> is <see langword="null" />.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 與這個 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> 類別之執行個體關聯的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />。

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can authenticate messages that are sent to message queues that require authentication, or messages can explicitly request authentication.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ 可以驗證傳送至需要驗證之訊息佇列的訊息，或訊息可以明確要求驗證。

trans-unit.source: The default authentication mode is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.
The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> values.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 與這個 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> 類別之執行個體關聯的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />。

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can encrypt messages on the wire when transferring messages between message queue managers.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ 可以在訊息佇列管理員之間傳輸訊息時，在線上加密訊息。

trans-unit.source: The default encryption algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.
The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> values.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 與這個 <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> 類別之執行個體關聯的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />。

trans-unit.source: The default protection level is <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.
The value is not one of the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> values.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 與這個 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> 類別之執行個體關聯的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />。

trans-unit.source: The default hash algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm.Sha1>.
The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> values.
